  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales and Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><p><u><strong>Social Media Management (Primary Responsibility)</strong></u></p><ul><li>Post and schedule content across social media platforms</li><li>Write basic captions and suggest simple content ideas</li><li>Capture photos and short videos during on-site visits</li><li>Monitor and respond to comments and direct messages</li><li>Perform basic optimisation such as posting timing and hashtag usage</li></ul><p><u><strong>Content Coordination</strong></u></p><ul><li>Coordinate bookings for photographers and videographers</li><li>Organise content shoots and logistics</li><li>Prepare shot lists based on line manager direction</li><li>Ensure creative assets are delivered on time</li><li>Maintain and organise the content library</li></ul><p><u><strong>Campaign Execution & Coordination</strong></u></p><ul><li>Publish promotional materials across digital platforms</li><li>Distribute campaign assets to outlets</li><li>Update promotions on delivery platforms</li><li>Follow up with outlets to obtain promotional setup photos</li><li>Track basic campaign performance</li></ul><p><u><strong>In-Store Marketing Support (Execution)</strong></u></p><ul><li>Send final artworks (prepared by design freelancers) to printers</li><li>Ensure marketing materials are delivered to all outlets</li><li>Assist with checking installation where required</li><li>Update line manager on outlet readiness and execution status</li></ul><p><u><strong>Menu Launch & Promotion Support</strong></u></p><ul><li>Upload new menu visuals and content</li><li>Post teasers and launch-related social media content</li><li>Coordinate influencer arrangements initiated by line manager</li><li>Distribute promotional kits to outlets</li></ul><p><u><strong>Delivery Platform Management</strong></u></p><ul><li>Update menu photos on GoFood, GrabFood, and ShopeeFood</li><li>Upload banners, promotional visuals, and promo codes</li><li>Track and monitor promotion activation</li></ul><p><u><strong>Reporting</strong></u></p><ul><li>Prepare monthly social media performance reports (followers, engagement, top posts)</li><li>Compile promotion redemption data provided by line manager or delivery platforms</li><li>Share basic customer observations and feedback</li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li>Degree in Marketing, Communications, Business, or related field</li><li>0–2 years of relevant experience; fresh graduates are welcome</li><li>Basic knowledge of social media platforms and content posting</li><li>Organised, detail-oriented, and able to coordinate multiple tasks</li><li>Willingness to perform on-site visits when required</li><li>Basic photo or video capture skills are an advantage</li></ul>",
